summary:
Currently self-employed as domestic construction worker running own business. Qualified electrician with college background.Responsible for the entire refurbishment and renovation process of residential property ranging from apartments to larger town houses, thus accustomed to long working hours and heavy physical labour.

Multilingual with fluency in Dutch, English and Polish, additionally conversational ability in the following: German and to a lesser extent Russian with ability to read Cyrillic.

Holds sailing and lifeguarding certificates.

Currently available and looking for offers/opportunities.
